data.description: Wonderful One story home in the Woodlake area with Solar Panels!  This 3 Bedroom, 2 Bath house has vinyl planking throughout home.  A new A/C unit (Lennox), a remodeled master bath that has a full stand up shower. The Primary closet has been remodeled with a California closet.  The back patio has been fully screened in.  The kitchen has beautiful Italian Granite counters with a 5.5' X 7' Granite Peninsula.  The Ceiling mounted Projection Movie camera with controller and refrigerator stays with the home. Nice fireplace in the living area.  The roof is 6 years old.
